title: All of Sony Got Hacked... Apparently...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a possible hacking of ALL of Sony and Playstation. With so much news and coverage about the subject I decided to delve deep into the mystery and discover that this was actually a case of a multibillion dollar company being scammed by some of the dumbest hacker's I've ever seen. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
